{"word":"G1715 - ἔμπροσθεν - émprosthen - em'-pros-then - Against","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἔμπροσθεν</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">émprosthen</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">em'-pros-then</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Against</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adverb / வினையடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"முன்னே, முதன்மை - வினையடை"},{"paragraph":"in front, before"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G4314 - πρός - prós - pros/4314\">G4314</a>; <i>in front of</i> (in place [literally or figuratively] or time): - against, at, before, (in presence, sight) of.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}